data.description: Seller will contribute up to $8,000 in closing cost assistance with acceptable offer! FHA financing available!  This 2 bedroom 1 bath house is a great starter home or would make a great investment to add to a portfolio. This house features a convenient carport and a spacious, fully fenced back yard. The interior boasts newer flooring and fresh interior paint, giving the home a modern and clean look. Additionally, the property offers a 2021 AC system and a 2019 roof, ensuring optimal comfort and functionality. The kitchen has been tastefully updated, providing a stylish and functional space for all your culinary needs. And the best part is this home has already been pre inspected and the 4 pt is available to view! Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home yours!
